org.transitime.db.structs

Class TravelTimesForPath

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.transitime.db.structs.TravelTimesForPath
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Entity
public class TravelTimesForPath
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Contains the expected time it takes to travel along the specified path, which is for one stop to another. There can be a different list of TravelTimesForPath for each trip. The idea is to share travel times when possible, when they are relatively the same for a trip pattern. But if a trip needs separate travel times then it can have it.
    Author:
    SkiBu Smith
